</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="62.[1442,2651,276,1852]" pageId="62" pageNumber="120">
<taxonomicName authority="Thomas, 1914" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1914" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Nyctimene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="120" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="vizcaccia" subSpecies="vizcaccia">N.v.vizcacciaThomas,1914—AdmiraltyIs(Manus)andBismarckArchipelago(NewIreland,NewBritain,andUmboiIs).</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="62.[1442,2651,276,1852]" pageId="62" pageNumber="120">
<taxonomicName authority="Troughton, 1936" authorityName="Troughton" authorityYear="1936" box="[1445,1917,402,427]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Nyctimene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="120" phylum="Chordata" rank="variety" species="vizcaccia" subSpecies="bougainville" variety="bougainville">N. v. bougainville Troughton, 1936</taxonomicName>
— Solomon Is (Buka, Bougainville, Fauro, Choiseul, Kolombangara, New 
<collectingCountry box="[1742,1856,433,466]" name="Georgia" pageId="62" pageNumber="120">Georgia</collectingCountry>
, Vangunu, Santa Isabel, and Guadalcanal).
